t\t<div class=\"space-content\"></div>\n\t<a id=\"main-content\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t<div class=\"container-fluid px-0\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row g-0\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"order-1 order-lg-2 col-12\">\n\t\t\t\t  <div class=\"region region-content\">\n    <div data-drupal-messages-fallback class=\"hidden\"></div>\n<div id=\"block-hoshizaki-bs5-breadcrumbs\" class=\"block block-system block-system-breadcrumb-block\">\n  \n    \n      \t<div class=\"mb-56\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container \">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2 id=\"system-breadcrumb\" class=\"visually-hidden\">パンくず</h2>\n\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"breadcrumb m-0\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/\" class=\"text-decoration-none\">ホーム</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tホシザキストーリー\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t</nav>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n  </div>\n<div id=\"block-hoshizaki-bs5-pagetitle\" class=\"block block-core block-page-title-block\">\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"page-title\"><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">ホシザキストーリー</span>\n</h1>\n\t\t\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n<div id=\"block-hoshizaki-bs5-content\" class=\"block block-system block-system-main-block\">\n  \n    \n      \n<article class=\"node node--type-page-builder node--view-mode-full\">\n\t<div class=\"node__content\">\n\t\t  <section class=\"bg-hoshizaki-story mt-0 container layout layout--onecol\">\n    <div  class=\"row layout__region layout__region--content\">\n      <div class=\"col\">\n        <div class=\"block block-layout-builder block-inline-blockbasic\">\n  \n    \n      \n            <div class=\"clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\">       <div class=\"d-flex flex-column text-image align-items-center flex-md-row-reverse\" style=\"\n  font-size: 1.12em;\n  line-height: 1.75;\n  gap: 2em;\n\">\n\n\n\n  <!-- Text -->\n  <div class=\"text-col d-flex flex-column\" style=\"\n    flex: 1 1 50%;\n    gap: 1.4em;\n  \">\n\n\n\n    <p class=\"mb-0\" style=\"\n      margin: 0;\n      font-size: 1em;\n    \">\n1947年の創業以来、ホシザキグループは卓越した生産技術とイノベーションを生み出し、それを実現する人材によって進化し続けてきました。 これからも企業理念の実践と品質の追求により、世界中の食を豊かにする製品とソリューションを創造していきます。\n    </p>\n\n   \n  </div>\n</div></div>\n      \n  </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"container layout layout--onecol\">\n    <div  class=\"row layout__region layout__region--content\">\n      <div class=\"col\">\n        <div class=\"block block-layout-builder block-inline-blockbasic\">\n  \n    \n      \n            <div class=\"clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\"><div class=\"d-flex flex-column text-image align-items-center flex-md-row-reverse\" style=\"\n  font-size: 1.12em;\n  line-height: 1.75;\n  gap: 2em;\n\">\n\n  <!-- Image -->\n  <div class=\"image-col\" style=\"\n    flex: 1 1 50%;\n  \">\n    <img\n      class=\"w-100 object-fit\"\n      src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-12/hoshizaki_ceo.jpg\"\n      alt=\"ceo\"\n      width=\"990\"\n      height=\"716\"\n      style=\"\n        display: block;\n        border-radius: 0.9em;\n      \"\n    >\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Text -->\n  <div class=\"text-col d-flex flex-column\" style=\"\n    flex: 1 1 50%;\n    gap: 1.4em;\n  \">\n\n    <h2 class=\"mb-0 text-primary\" style=\"\n      font-size: 1.8em;\n      line-height: 1.15;\n      font-weight: 400;\n    \">\n      トップメッセージ\n    </h2>\n\n    <p class=\"mb-0\" style=\"\n      margin: 0;\n      font-size: 1em;\n    \">\n     ホシザキは「オリジナル製品を持たない企業に飛躍はない」をモットーに、\n      モノづくりの「極限への挑戦」を果敢に続け、新しい技術と創造力で、\n      さまざまな製品を世に送りだしてきました。\n    </p>\n        <div class=\"d-flex\">\n            <a class=\"btn\" href=\"/story/message\">メッセージを見る</a>\n        </div>\n\n\n  </div>\n</div></div>\n      \n  </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"container layout layout--onecol\">\n    <div  class=\"row layout__region layout__region--content\">\n      <div class=\"col\">\n        <div class=\"block block-layout-builder block-inline-blockbasic\">\n  \n    \n      \n            <div class=\"clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\"><div class=\"d-flex flex-column text-image align-items-center flex-md-row\" style=\"\n  font-size: 1.12em;\n  line-height: 1.75;\n  gap: 2em;\n\">\n\n  <!-- Image -->\n  <div class=\"image-col\" style=\"\n    flex: 1 1 50%;\n  \">\n    <img\n      class=\"w-100 object-fit\"\n      src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-01/philosophy_plant_0.jpg\"\n      alt=\"ceo\"\n      width=\"990\"\n      height=\"716\"\n      style=\"\n        display: block;\n        border-radius: 0.9em;\n      \"\n    >\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Text -->\n  <div class=\"text-col d-flex flex-column\" style=\"\n    flex: 1 1 50%;\n    gap: 1.4em;\n  \">\n\n    <h2 class=\"mb-0 text-primary\" style=\"\n      font-size: 1.8em;\n      line-height: 1.15;\n      font-weight: 400;\n    \">\n      企業理念\n    </h2>\n\n    <p class=\"mb-0\" style=\"\n      margin: 0;\n      font-size: 1em;\n    \">\n      経営計画を含むすべての事業活動の原点であり、グループ社員全員が実践していくことで、社会へ価値を創造していきます。\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"d-flex\">\n      <a class=\"btn\" href=\"/story/corporate-philosophy\">企業理念を見る</a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n      \n  </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"container layout layout--onecol\">\n    <div  class=\"row layout__region layout__region--content\">\n      <div class=\"col\">\n        <div class=\"block block-layout-builder block-inline-blockbasic\">\n  \n    \n      \n            <div class=\"clearfix text-formatted field 